\c 93
\s Jehovha ndiye Mambo mukuru
\p
\v 1 Jehovha anobata ushe; akafuka umambo; Jehovha akafuka simba, akazvisunga chiuno naro; Nyikawo yakateyiwa,
\s haingazununguswi.
\p
\v 2 Chigaro chenyu choushe chakasimbiswa kubva kare; Imi muripo kubva pakusingaperi.
\p
\v 3 Jehovha, nzizi dzakanzwisa. Nzizi dzakanzwisa manzwi adzo; Nzizi dzinonzwisa kutinhira
\s kwadzo.
\p
\v 4 Jehovha anokunda mazwi emvura zhinji,
\s Namafungu ane simba egungwa, Jehovha, ari kumusoro, ndiye ane simba.
\p
\v 5 Zvipupuriro zvenyu
\s ndezvamazvokwadi kwazvo; Utsvene unofanira imba yenyu, Jehovha, nokusingaperi.
